      "role": "user",
      "content": "The QuickResponse system is fine for the standard stuff, we don't need 'elegance' for simple password resets or shipping updates. We're looking at a huge reduction in operational overhead. Why do you think it's going to struggle with the complexity? Give me a concrete reason why we shouldn't just switch to the templates.",
